[http://www.tenda.cn/tendacn/Product/show.aspx?productid=396 Product page] "10016740", "V1.0", and a lead-free logo is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. The same board would appear to be used by the [[Tenda F303]]. :The BCM5357C0 is marked w/ the '''Broadcom''' logo, ''BCM5357C0KFBG'', ''HE1318 P30'', ''286355 01B W''. The default SSID format is presumed to be '''Tenda_XXXXXX''' (it's in the FCC manual). The power adapter shown in the FCC external photos is a '''Shenzhen Heweishun Network Technology''' TEA09-09060 (100-240VAC ~ 50/60Hz, 0.3A -> 9VDC, 0.6A).
